cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI 

The paper discusses the application of computer vision and machine learning techniques for automated rock typing, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of feature extraction and convolutional neural networks also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of color distribution, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR).
